00:22:16,835 --> 00:22:18,235
That's why, the more so.

458
00:22:18,235 --> 00:22:20,535
If he just got mixed up in this,

459
00:22:20,535 --> 00:22:23,735
Conan would probably contact us saying not to worry,

460
00:22:23,735 --> 00:22:25,735
but if not...

461
00:22:25,735 --> 00:22:31,035
It's highly likely that he's also a suspect for something.

462
00:22:31,035 --> 00:22:33,331
Genta's father.

463
00:22:33,535 --> 00:22:35,635
What?

464
00:22:38,235 --> 00:22:40,035
Dad.

